beer.beer_description: Rosé Champagne meets IPA. This collab between Frenchies Brewery and Bridge Road Brewers is extra fruity with fresh raspberries added, along with pale malts and loads of Enigma hops. Zero bitterness, dry finish, and distinctive raspberry aromas. Brewed for GABS 2019.. and nope, there is no grapes or wine in this beer! Just Outstanding Flavours! Vote for 44!!
